 Minutes of UTC Meeting 162|date=2020-01-23|first=Lisa|last=Moore|section=B.13.4 Changes to Identifier_Type of some Unicode 13.0 characters}}\n|- class=\"sortbottom\"\n| colspan=\"6\" | {{reflist|group=lower-alpha|refs=<ref name=final>Proposed code points and characters names may differ from final code points and names</ref>}}\n|}\n\n== See also ==\n* [[Sinhala Archaic Numbers|Sinhala Archaic Numbers (Unicode block)]]\n\n== References ==\n{{reflist}}\n\n{{Sinhala language}}\n\n[[Category:Unicode blocks]]\n[[Category:Sinhala script]]\n", "name_user": "43.228.110.3", "label": "unsafe", "comment": "(\u2192\u200eSee also:Fixed grammar, Added links)", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sinhala_(Unicode_block)"}
